rue}} if this input event matches a pre-defined action of any type.=== is_action_pressed ===*  bool '''is_action_pressed''' '''(''' [[StringName GD|StringName]] action, bool allow_echo=false ''')''' constReturns {{Span|true}} if the given action is being pressed (and is not an echo event for [[InputEventKey GD|InputEventKey]] events, unless {{Span|allow_echo}} is {{Span|true}}). Not relevant for events of type [[InputEventMouseMotion GD|InputEventMouseMotion]] or [[InputEventScreenDrag GD|InputEventScreenDrag]].=== is_action_released ===*  bool '''is_action_released''' '''(''' [[StringName GD|StringName]] action ''')''' constReturns {{Span|true}} if the given action is released (i.e. not pressed). Not relevant for events of type [[InputEventMouseMotion GD|InputEventMouseMotion]] or [[InputEventScreenDrag GD|InputEventScreenDrag]].=== is_action_type ===*  bool '''is_action_type ( )''' constReturns {{Span|true}} if this input event's type is one that can be assigned to an input action.=== is_echo ===*  bool '''is_echo ( )''' constReturns {{Span|true}} if this input event is an echo event (only for events of type [[InputEventKey GD|InputEventKey]]).=== is_pressed ===*  bool '''is_pressed ( )''' constReturns {{Span|true}} if this input event is pressed. Not relevant for events of type [[InputEventMouseMotion GD|InputEventMouseMotion]] or [[InputEventScreenDrag GD|InputEventScreenDrag]].=== shortcut_match ===*  bool '''shortcut_match''' '''(''' [[InputEvent GD|InputEvent]] event ''')''' constReturns {{Span|true}} if the given input event is checking for the same key ([[InputEventKey GD|InputEventKey]]), button ([[InputEventJoypadButton GD|InputEventJoypadButton]]) or action ([[InputEventAction GD|InputEventAction]]).=== xformed_by ===*  [[InputEvent GD|InputEvent]] '''xformed_by''' '''(''' [[Transform2D GD|Transform2D]] xform, [[Vector2 GD|Vector2]] local_ofs=Vector2( 0, 0 ) ''')''' constReturns a copy of the given input event which has been offset by {{Span|local_ofs}} and transformed by {{Span|xform}}. Relevant for events of type [[InputEventMouseButton GD|InputEventMouseButton]], [[InputEventMouseMotion GD|InputEventMouseMotion]], [[InputEventScreenTouch GD|InputEventScreenTouch]], [[InputEventScreenDrag GD|InputEventScreenDrag]], [[InputEventMagnifyGesture GD|InputEventMagnifyGesture]] and [[InputEventPanGesture GD|InputEventPanGesture]].